rong>Shattered Star：</strong>破碎魔星<br><strong>Skull &amp; Shackles：</strong>颅骨与镣铐<br><strong>Strange Aeons：</strong>万古奇诡<br><strong>Tyrant&#039;s Grasp：</strong>暴君魔爪<br><strong>War of the Crown：</strong>王冠战争<br><strong>Wrath of the Righteous：</strong>正义之怒<br></span><hr /><span style="font-size: 12pt;" class="bbc_size"><strong>Alchemical Remedies：</strong>炼金药品<br><strong>Armor：</strong>防具<br><strong>Aura：</strong>灵氲<br><strong>Bearer ：</strong>携带者<br><strong>Carried：</strong><br><strong>Competence ：</strong>表现（加值）<br><strong>Greater：</strong><br><strong>Hold：</strong>持有<br><strong>Lesser：</strong><br><strong>Masterwork：</strong>精<strong>制</strong>品<br><strong>Major：</strong><br><strong>Minor：</strong><br><strong>Normal：</strong><br><strong>Owner：</strong>拥有者<br><strong>possession：</strong><br><strong>Retrieving a stored item：</strong><br><strong>Varies：</strong>各异<br><strong>Weapon：</strong>武器<br><strong>Wear：</strong>穿戴<br><strong>Wearer：</strong>穿戴者<br><strong>Wield：</strong>持用<br><strong>Wielder：</strong>持用者<br></span><hr /><span style="font-size: 12pt;" class="bbc_size"><strong>Acrobatics：</strong>特技动作<br><strong>Appraise：</strong>估价<br><strong>Bluff：</strong>唬骗<br><strong>Climb：</strong>攀爬<br><strong>Craft：</strong>工艺<br><strong>Diplomacy：</strong>交涉<br><strong>Disable Device：</strong>解除装置<br><strong>Disguise：</strong>易容<br><strong>Escape Artist：</strong>逃脱<br><strong>Fly：</strong>飞行<br><strong>Handle Animal：</strong>驯养动物<br><strong>Heal：</strong>医疗<br><strong>Intimidate：</strong>威吓<br><strong>Knowledge (Arcana)：</strong>知识（神秘）<br><strong>Knowledge (Dungeoneering)：</strong>知识（地城）<br><strong>Knowledge (Engineerinj)：</strong>知识（工程学）<br><strong>Knowledge (Geography)：</strong>知识（地理）<br><strong>Knowledge (History)：</strong>知识（历史）<br><strong>Knowledge (Local)：</strong>知识（地方）<br><strong>Knowledge (Nature)：</strong>知识（自然）<br><strong>Knowledge (Nobility)：</strong>知识（贵族）<br><strong>Knowledge (Planes)：</strong>知识（位面）<br><strong>Knowledge (Religion)：</strong>知识（宗教）<br><strong>Linguistics：</strong>语言学<br>　<strong>Aboleth：</strong>底栖魔鱼语<br>　<strong>Abyssal：</strong>深渊语<br>　<strong>Aklo：</strong>邪灵语<br>　<strong>Aquan：</strong>水族语<br>　<strong>Auran：</strong>气族语<br>　<strong>Boggard：</strong><br>　<strong>Celestial：</strong>天界语<br>　<strong>Common：</strong>通用语<br>　<strong>Cyclops：</strong>独眼巨人语<br>　<strong>Dark Folk：</strong><br>　<strong>Draconic：</strong>龙语<br>　<strong>Drow Sign Language：</strong>卓尔手语<br>　<strong>Druidic：</strong>德鲁依语<br>　<strong>Dwarven：</strong>矮人语<br>　<strong>D’ziriak：</strong><br>　<strong>Elven：</strong>精灵语<br>　<strong>Giant：</strong>巨人语<br>　<strong>Gnoll：</strong>豺狼人语<br>　<strong>Gnome：</strong>侏儒语<br>　<strong>Goblin：</strong>地精语<br>　<strong>Grippli：</strong><br>　<strong>Halfling：</strong>半身人语<br>　<strong>Ignan：</strong>火族语<br>　<strong>Infernal：</strong>炼狱语<br>　<strong>Necril：</strong><br>　<strong>Orc：</strong>兽人语<br>　<strong>Protean：</strong><br>　<strong>Sphinx：</strong><br>　<strong>Sylvan：</strong>风族语<br>　<strong>Tengu：</strong>天狗语<br>　<strong>Terran：</strong>土族语<br>　<strong>Treant：</strong>树人语<br>　<strong>Undercommon：</strong>地底通用语<br>　<strong>Vegepygmy：</strong><br><strong>Perception：</strong>察觉<br><strong>Perform：</strong>表演<br>　<strong>Act：</strong><br>　　<strong>comedy：</strong><br>　　<strong>drama：</strong><br>　　<strong>pantomime：</strong><br>　<strong>Comedy：</strong><br>　　<strong>buffoonery：</strong><br>　　<strong>limericks：</strong><br>　　<strong>joke-telling：</strong>　　<br>　<strong>Dance：</strong><br>　　<strong>ballet：</strong><br>　　<strong>waltz：</strong><br>　　<strong>jig：</strong><br>　<strong>Keyboard instruments：</strong><br>　　<strong>harpsichord：</strong><br>　　<strong>piano：</strong><br>　　<strong>pipe organ：</strong><br>　<strong>Oratory：</strong><br>　　<strong>epic：</strong><br>　　<strong>ode：</strong><br>　　<strong>storytelling：</strong>　　<br>　<strong>Percussion instruments：</strong><br>　　<strong>bells：</strong><br>　　<strong>chimes：</strong><br>　　<strong>drums：</strong><br>　　<strong>gong：</strong>　　<br>　<strong>S